reviewText: Grand boys was excited to receive!!

The kids loved it!!!

It came even faster than scheduled which was super nice made the kids even more happy!!

I would recommend it for the kids!!
DVDs are great content wise. There are lots of skips that makes at least one episode unwatchable. Disappointing but Son loves the ones he can watch.

I had to give it a perfect rating becuase it was the cartoon ever, I'm a person who knows a good cartoon and a good show and this cartoon show of Geronimo Stilton is a good show. I read most of the books and wondered for a while what the cartoon was like and the cartoon seems to be a bit better because it has a fluid animated view of the show and characters. If your passionate for cartoons, this is one of the best ones to see. I'm so glad I found it that I felt like I struck gold.
I love this it's great and sence I got this I have not watch eney thing eles and it's the best deal i've had  p.s. each volume comes with 2 dvd's
